\section{THE SIGNATURES}
We provide two structures:
\begin{description}
\item[Utf8]
provides generic support for converting UTF-8 encoded strings into Unicode code points, represented
using {\em Word.WORD}.
\item[PPUnicode]
supports translation between the {\Product} extended character set and Unicode code points.
